  "texts": [
    "This approach should prioritize AI literacy among educators and students [18]; [19].",
    "GenAI serves both Teachers and Students in Different WaysThere is an increasing need to understand the relevance, utility, and limitations of its use in Education at all levels.",
    "ChatGPT, often regarded as a Swiss Army Knife for educators, embodies a multifaceted tool capable of transforming educational practices across lesson planning, instruction, assessment, and communication [20]; [21]; [22]; [23].",
    "It helps the teacher in lesson planning [24]; [25].ChatGPT can set relevant IEP and SMART (Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Results-oriented or relevant, and Time-bound) goals using its vast knowledge base.",
    "ChatGPT can write these goals and assist teachers."
